messages.text: Yeah I think I locked myself in fridge
R u in the fridge or freezer?
No he left just after you did
I had to put away the trays of fish
Do you know how late it is?
You have to come back and get me out of here
Start doing jumping jacks or something lol
You should have waited for me
Screw that. It’s not my fault
I put the trays in here FOR YOU
Roger told YOU to do it, not me
This stuff happens to me all the time
I’m getting closer but I don’t have the key
I’m sure you already knew that
What?!!! You don’t have the key!!!
Roger gave it to me just before he left
There might be an accident up ahead tho
Can you get a hold of Roger?
Did you try yelling and hitting the door tho?
If I had his number I’d call him
Well I don’t have his number
If I get out of here I’m never eating fish again
I don’t think I’ll be able to talk
My mouth is chattering too much
Can I eat the frozen fish?
I think I hear a siren
I’m gonna kick in the front door
